WEBVTT

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:40.280
The Trastuzumab and Ramucirumab are both gone.

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:47.120
If I tell you, don't get upset.

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:47.640
Huh?

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:50.959
Think about it, once your wife gets pregnant,

00:01:50.959 --> 00:01:52.840
the financial pressure will be huge, right?

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:56.799
Those two medications are insanely expensive.

00:01:57.079 --> 00:02:00.159
I told the doctor to stop them.

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:03.760
The pregnancy thing isn't even on the horizon yet.

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:05.200
And besides, your illness is almost cured.

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:06.799
You can't stop this medication.

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:10.759
Your dad is just being hard on himself.

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:13.759
He feels he can't earn enough money

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:15.280
and that he's burdening you.

00:02:20.439 --> 00:02:21.919
Actually, I...

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:25.240
have some good news I haven't told you.

00:02:25.240 --> 00:02:26.800
What good news?

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:31.919
I got promoted to Assistant Branch Manager.

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:33.879
Really?

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:38.360
It's true, I got the promotion.

00:02:38.759 --> 00:02:39.439
So,

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:42.840
from now on, you focus on your job at the bank,

00:02:42.919 --> 00:02:43.719
and I...

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:45.840
will focus on writing my script.

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:49.680
This is the concept for a new script.

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:50.560
Okay, okay, stop, stop.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:51.479
Come here, let me talk to you.

00:02:51.479 --> 00:02:52.240
Stop.

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:54.879
You're not tired, but darn it, I am.

00:02:55.759 --> 00:02:56.560
Alright, alright.

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:58.319
You're always cutting me off.

00:02:58.319 --> 00:02:59.039
Enough.

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:01.680
When is Xiaoshi coming back?

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:04.199
She probably can't stand it there either, soon.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.599
That's great.

00:03:09.479 --> 00:03:10.560
Here, I...

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:14.639
got some new medicine from Dr. Wu.

00:03:14.719 --> 00:03:16.599
Specifically to nourish your health.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:17.840
Remember to take it.

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:22.360
Try to give us a big, healthy grandson next year.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.479
I'm not some baby-making machine.

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:26.599
Mom, about that...

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:29.039
And Dad, listen to me.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:31.680
I'm earning a lot more now than before.

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:35.199
We can use this medication however we want.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:36.680
Promise me.

00:03:37.479 --> 00:03:38.560
You rascal.

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:40.360
Listen to your mom about what we just discussed.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:41.039
I know, I know.

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.800
You've been an employee for so many years.

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:50.719
Always letting the younger ones get ahead of you.

00:03:50.719 --> 00:03:51.759
Let me tell you,

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:53.560
figure out a way to secure Director Qiu's business, fast.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:55.680
Otherwise, don't bother coming to work.

00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:01.120
The promotion opportunity this time

00:04:01.639 --> 00:04:02.879
will be given to Xiao Jia.

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:15.919
Manager Tong.

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:22.720
Get in the car.

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:27.600
You should at least introduce your products to me.

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.399
Get in and we'll talk.

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:56.639
L-Let's just g-get

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:57.680
straight to the p-p-point.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.519
Why are you so naive?

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:03.879
Um, the driver, h-he...

00:05:03.879 --> 00:05:04.800
He's not d-down

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.560
n-not, not hot.

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:07.839
He can c-come up.

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:09.879
So, l-let me, let me

00:05:09.879 --> 00:05:11.279
briefly introduce a

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:12.120
financial product to you.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:14.040
Although the short-term return rate isn't high,

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:15.439
if held long-term,

00:05:15.439 --> 00:05:17.040
the returns are still considerable.

00:05:20.759 --> 00:05:22.360
Weren't you looking for a deposit?

00:05:22.439 --> 00:05:23.319
Is this enough?

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:31.240
Y-You...

00:05:33.439 --> 00:05:35.160
Wh-what, what do you mean?

00:05:35.160 --> 00:05:36.720
I... I...

00:05:37.639 --> 00:05:39.720
I... I have a wife.

00:05:40.439 --> 00:05:41.519
That's okay.

00:05:41.959 --> 00:05:43.279
I have a husband too.

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:49.279
Um, um, sis... sis...

00:05:49.279 --> 00:05:50.160
Sis is here, sis is here.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:52.120
S-say hello to your brother-in-law for me.

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:56.360
This, I'm really just

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:57.319
simply

00:05:57.319 --> 00:05:59.600
selling this financial product, so...

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:01.680
I get it, I get it.

00:06:02.279 --> 00:06:04.439
Just an opening line, sis understands.

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:07.279
Right?

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:09.680
Director Qiu, I...

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:11.360
love my wife very much.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:13.639
And I d-don't want to be the other man.

00:06:17.480 --> 00:06:19.720
You're so adorable.

00:06:20.399 --> 00:06:22.439
What 'other man' nonsense.

00:06:23.199 --> 00:06:24.160
Look, Director Qiu,

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:25.279
I think that...

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.279
if y-you have b-business,

00:06:27.279 --> 00:06:29.920
y-you, c-come to our bank to talk.

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:32.439
Sorry.

00:06:54.639 --> 00:06:55.759
Listen, Tongtong,

00:06:56.079 --> 00:06:57.439
you're wandering around every day

00:06:57.439 --> 00:06:58.759
with no real job.

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:02.439
I did say I supported you coming back to develop here,

00:07:02.439 --> 00:07:04.639
but I didn't say I'd support you mooching off your parents.

00:07:05.519 --> 00:07:07.199
This *is* my real job.

00:07:07.199 --> 00:07:08.000
What did you think?

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:09.360
This is my job.

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:10.519
This?

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:12.040
A crappy camera?

00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:13.399
How is that any different from those

00:07:13.399 --> 00:07:15.040
influencers who just travel and take photos?

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.160
What's the difference?

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:18.120
No wonder your mom keeps urging you to go back.

00:07:19.279 --> 00:07:21.000
If you keep this up,

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.480
I'll take your mom's side.

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:23.560
You don't understand.

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:24.240
You don't understand anything.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.600
Fine, fine, stop filming me.

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:36.439
Alright, after this drink, that's it.

00:07:36.439 --> 00:07:37.519
Don't drink anymore.

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:40.240
No matter how pathetic you are, can you be more pathetic than me?

00:07:41.879 --> 00:07:42.600
Big brother.

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:44.160
Have you eaten?

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:44.920
I have.

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.199
Qiu'er.

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:46.839
Perfect timing, have some ribbonfish.

00:07:46.839 --> 00:07:48.240
Are you moving?

00:07:51.279 --> 00:07:52.480
Let me tell you guys.

00:07:54.439 --> 00:07:56.279
As soon as Ma Weiguo moved back in,

00:07:56.279 --> 00:07:58.720
he's trying to force me and my parents out.

00:08:00.079 --> 00:08:01.720
Isn't he going too far?

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:03.199
How does he have the nerve to do this?

00:08:03.279 --> 00:08:05.839
See, even Jin Tong can't stand it.

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:08.959
I say, on the pillar of historical shame,

00:08:08.959 --> 00:08:10.560
there's a tiny little section,

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:11.639
that's all reserved for him.

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:13.199
Stop with the wisecracks.

00:08:13.199 --> 00:08:15.639
Do you have any ideas to help Qiu'er out?

00:08:17.120 --> 00:08:18.360
I actually do have an idea.

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.800
I can chase him away.

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:23.680
Alright, alright, don't make things worse.

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:24.600
You should head back now.

00:08:24.600 --> 00:08:25.439
How am I making things worse?

00:08:25.439 --> 00:08:27.519
Go back and fiddle with your camera. Go on, get out.

00:08:27.519 --> 00:08:28.519
I just sat down.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:29.560
Go back, hurry up.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:30.879
Have some tea.

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:35.960
Qiu'er.

00:08:36.519 --> 00:08:39.200
Don't worry, Big Brother and I will think of something.

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:41.919
I refuse to believe he can get the better of us.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.720
But look, this house belongs to him.

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:46.080
What can I say?

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:46.799
There's nothing to be done.

00:08:46.799 --> 00:08:47.240
No, wait.

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:49.759
I'm telling you, don't worry about this.

00:08:49.879 --> 00:08:51.279
You have work tomorrow, right?

00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:53.000
Finish this drink and get back home.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:55.000
I still have to deal with that brat Feifei.

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:56.679
Drink less.

00:08:56.679 --> 00:08:57.559
Right.

00:09:01.159 --> 00:09:03.759
I think life is full of surprises.

00:09:03.759 --> 00:09:05.240
Surprises are everywhere.

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:07.919
Take me, for example, back in the day.

00:09:07.919 --> 00:09:08.720
Back then,

00:09:08.919 --> 00:09:12.879
just so my parents could live more spaciously,

00:09:12.879 --> 00:09:14.600
I moved out of the hutong.

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:17.600
Took on a loan, gritted my teeth, and bought a relocation apartment.

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:18.720
That was for my parents.

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:19.759
Make it bigger.

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:22.679
My wife and I rented a smaller one.

00:09:23.639 --> 00:09:28.840
Then one day, my dad got sick.

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:32.240
He said he wanted to live back in the hutong.

00:09:32.759 --> 00:09:35.039
Said he wanted to die in the hutong too.

00:09:35.039 --> 00:09:35.919
Alright then.

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:38.559
Let's move then, let you go back to the hutong.

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:41.519
And from then on,

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:46.159
I've been running back and forth.

00:09:47.919 --> 00:09:49.120
Back and forth.

00:09:51.399 --> 00:09:52.639
Back and forth.

00:09:57.399 --> 00:09:58.320
Second Brother.

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:04.240
Big Brother.

00:10:28.039 --> 00:10:30.120
Have you come up with that new plan yet?

00:10:30.120 --> 00:10:31.080
Is he asleep?

00:10:31.279 --> 00:10:32.799
He's asleep, keep your voice down.

00:10:35.639 --> 00:10:36.559
The new plan?

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:39.200
I think it's still not quite mature.

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:40.759
No, tell me about it first.

00:10:40.759 --> 00:10:41.440
Let me hear it.

00:10:42.679 --> 00:10:44.120
Anyway, no matter what,

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:46.039
I'm getting him into university.

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:50.279
If you ask me,

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:52.159
you should stop giving our son such a hard time.

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:55.200
With your junior high school education level,

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:56.879
can you really manage him?

00:10:58.000 --> 00:11:00.120
I've been learning a lot lately,

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:02.519
about communicating with kids

00:11:02.519 --> 00:11:03.799
and education-related

00:11:03.799 --> 00:11:04.919
new theories.

00:11:04.919 --> 00:11:06.159
I have to say, they're quite interesting.

00:11:06.159 --> 00:11:07.679
I'll try putting them into practice later.

00:11:07.919 --> 00:11:09.720
What's the use of just theoretical knowledge?

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:11.720
The kid's grown up now, right?

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:16.559
Maybe we should just go along with him a bit.

00:11:16.559 --> 00:11:17.840
No, look, you're doing it again.

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:19.679
How many times have I said it?

00:11:20.759 --> 00:11:22.039
We can go along with him on other things,

00:11:22.639 --> 00:11:25.440
but going to university, he must listen to me.

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:28.039
We have to be a united front, you know?

00:11:28.039 --> 00:11:29.399
I'm putting this out there.

00:11:30.039 --> 00:11:31.320
About going to university,

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:34.279
someday both of you will thank me.

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.600
Fine, fine, you're the expert.

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:37.679
Just as long as in the future,

00:11:37.679 --> 00:11:39.639
you stop always threatening and yelling at our son.

00:11:39.639 --> 00:11:40.759
I know.

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:45.039
Haven't I already started this

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:46.799
carrot-and-stick approach?

00:11:47.039 --> 00:11:47.759
Right?

00:11:50.559 --> 00:11:51.840
All these shoes of his.

00:11:53.039 --> 00:11:54.120
Buys so many.

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:55.480
Spends all day not focusing on proper work.

00:11:55.799 --> 00:11:57.320
Look at these pairs.

00:11:57.840 --> 00:12:00.360
I take care of these better than I do my own face.

00:12:09.039 --> 00:12:11.200
Uh, I'm going to go wash my hands.

00:13:00.679 --> 00:13:02.039
What are you doing? It's the middle of the night.

00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:03.279
You reek of alcohol.

00:13:03.559 --> 00:13:04.879
I need to discuss something with you.

00:13:04.879 --> 00:13:05.679
I disagree.

00:13:06.600 --> 00:13:07.759
I haven't even said it yet.

00:13:07.759 --> 00:13:08.919
I won't agree to anything you say.

00:13:08.919 --> 00:13:10.000
Here's the thing.

00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:11.840
I'm just exhausted today.

00:13:11.840 --> 00:13:13.960
A designated driver back to the Fifth Ring Road is too expensive.

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.960
Can I just crash here for the night?

00:13:16.679 --> 00:13:17.279
No.

00:13:17.799 --> 00:13:19.039
You're so heartless.

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:19.639
How dare you...

00:13:19.639 --> 00:13:20.480
Who said you could come in?

00:13:22.279 --> 00:13:23.200
What are you doing?

00:13:23.639 --> 00:13:25.000
Who said you could just lie on my bed?

00:13:25.000 --> 00:13:25.919
Have you even showered?

00:13:26.039 --> 00:13:26.759
Yes, I have.

00:13:26.759 --> 00:13:27.600
Why are you so germophobic now?

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:28.480
Get down.

00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:30.639
Get down!

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:31.840
What are you doing?

00:13:31.840 --> 00:13:33.679
It's not like we didn't sleep together as kids.

00:13:33.679 --> 00:13:34.879
Why are you being so distant?

00:13:34.879 --> 00:13:35.759
That was then.

00:13:35.759 --> 00:13:36.399
This is now.

00:13:36.399 --> 00:13:37.240
How old are you this year?

00:13:37.240 --> 00:13:38.240
I'm younger than you, anyway.

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:39.919
Don't worry.

00:13:39.919 --> 00:13:42.799
When I sleep, I'm all about being quiet.

00:13:43.440 --> 00:13:44.279
Just go to sleep.

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:47.399
Relax. Just relax.

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:53.600
Your pillow is pretty comfortable.

00:13:57.840 --> 00:13:59.919
We've received word.

00:13:59.919 --> 00:14:03.840
Key trading partners may impose additional tariffs in the future.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:06.879
The company needs to prepare for both scenarios.

00:14:06.960 --> 00:14:11.039
While attracting foreign capital back,

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:14.440
the board has tentatively decided

00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:18.600
to shift the strategic focus to overseas markets next quarter.

00:14:18.600 --> 00:14:20.559
China and India

00:14:20.559 --> 00:14:22.639
are the priority targets.

00:14:22.759 --> 00:14:24.440
Chris, over to you.

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:26.039
Okay.

00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:27.639
Everyone,

00:14:27.639 --> 00:14:31.879
our department's investigation into the Asian market is as follows.

00:14:31.960 --> 00:14:33.879
As of 6 PM yesterday,

00:14:34.080 --> 00:14:36.399
our domestic revenue in China this month

00:14:36.399 --> 00:14:37.960
continues to show a downward trend.

00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:40.519
Our revenue in India is also declining.

00:14:40.519 --> 00:14:41.679
It's decreased year-on-year by...

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:49.879
Chris, please continue.

00:14:50.840 --> 00:14:51.440
Sorry.

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:52.440
Currently,

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.840
these two countries'

00:14:53.840 --> 00:14:56.559
domestic high-tech industries are developing rapidly.

00:15:01.919 --> 00:15:03.399
Excuse me, Martin.

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:05.720
Your microphone seems to have a problem.

00:15:05.720 --> 00:15:06.799
If you don't mind,

00:15:06.799 --> 00:15:08.720
you can reply to us in text.

00:15:10.320 --> 00:15:11.679
Okay.

00:15:11.759 --> 00:15:13.320
We recommend

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:15.080
expanding the scale of the two branch offices

00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:16.720
to four companies.

00:15:16.720 --> 00:15:20.519
Establish new subsidiaries

00:15:20.519 --> 00:15:22.440
in Guangzhou, China, and Chennai, India.

00:15:53.879 --> 00:15:55.399
Sis Li, watering the flowers?

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:57.879
Want to play a game?

00:15:58.000 --> 00:15:59.039
Come on, come on.

00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:13.279
Weiguo.

00:16:13.279 --> 00:16:14.759
Weiguo, wait, wait, wait.

00:16:14.759 --> 00:16:15.360
Uncle Tong.

00:16:15.679 --> 00:16:16.360
So,

00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:18.080
did you sleep comfortably last night?

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:18.679
It was okay.

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:22.080
You have to admit, living in this courtyard house is more comfortable.

00:16:22.080 --> 00:16:22.679
Right?

00:16:22.679 --> 00:16:23.000
Yes.

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:23.360
See?

00:16:23.360 --> 00:16:24.600
Wait, wait, wait.

00:16:25.399 --> 00:16:26.960
My son, Qiu'er,

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:29.919
wanted me to move into their apartment building a couple years ago.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:31.960
I felt so cooped up there.

00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:33.200
Come back for lunch at noon.

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:33.639
Alright.

00:16:33.639 --> 00:16:34.639
I'm waiting to have a drink with you.

00:16:34.639 --> 00:16:35.080
Sure.

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:44.159
You...

