The extra time...

00:41:36.360 --> 00:41:38.199
...could be used to take care of our dad, right?

00:41:38.320 --> 00:41:40.000
Do I have to spell it out for you?

00:41:40.000 --> 00:41:41.360
I can't bear to be apart from you.

00:41:42.360 --> 00:41:44.199
I can't bear to be apart from you either.

00:41:45.039 --> 00:41:46.039
So what you're saying is,

00:41:46.039 --> 00:41:47.840
if we had a big house right now,

